    "Step 3: Experimentation with Integrated CNNs + DWT + SVM.",
    "Additionally, we outline the final stratum of the PolynetDWTCADx system architecture, which includes CNN-incorporated SVM models.",
    "In scenarios where the dataset is highly dimensional and easily partitioned into classes, SVMs are particularly advantageous.",
